{"tid":2171184,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好空虛","createTime":"2020-08-23T19:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T16:47:35.000Z","uid":364562,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed67887724b0dd4f57b2bae6a06b52854eca854","tid":2171184,"uid":364562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T19:24:57.000Z","msg":"做咩都無興趣，完全無個人嗜好。<br />\n26歲，己婚，無咩朋友，有心事搵唔到人傾計。<br />\n同事基本係女性居多，傾下計都會被老婆剷到飛起。<br />\n<br />\n人越大，顧慮越多，連打機都有罪惡感。<br />\n以前啲豬朋狗友仲係打機，飲酒，賭錢，溝女，<br />\n而家仲個個咩住10幾萬債，覺得同佢哋越黎越遠。<br />\n<br />\n個人好空虛，唔知自己為咩生存。"},{"pid":"6cfffc150f93e7f3fd6261831ad643801016cee2","tid":2171184,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T21:56:04.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"cb7df8d59d858b1747ab064413ffa7e9ee7df9b3","tid":2171184,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T21:57:29.000Z","msg":"咁你想點呀"},{"pid":"2b24114557cd887ac393bd568b68f4088c1d323c","tid":2171184,"uid":367708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T02:10:25.000Z","msg":"單身都同你一樣"},{"pid":"2b6833d9b4c52f80ecd719995847a9b3943f1bb8","tid":2171184,"uid":9467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:28:55.000Z","msg":"有拖拍都同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018f222fa11c9ec1189435f26f78704d9545a054","tid":2171184,"uid":364562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T16:47:35.000Z","msg":"人越黎越大，朋友越黎越少。<br />\n越嚟越唔敢深交，係咪香港人寫照？"}]}